<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f7; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .header { background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: 28px 32px; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .body { padding: 28px 32px; color: #374151; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 18px 0; }
    .info-table td { padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .info-table td:first-child { font-weight: bold; color: #6b7280; width: 36%; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 99px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
    .footer { padding: 18px 32px; background: #f9fafb; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>&#128424; Print Job Confirmed</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Hi, your print job was successfully processed.</p>
    <table class="info-table">
      <tr><td>File</td><td>{{ filename }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Printer</td><td>{{ printer }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Sender</td><td>{{ sender }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Status</td><td><span class="badge">{{ status }}</span></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Job ID</td><td>{{ job_id }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Time</td><td>{{ timestamp }}</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p style="color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;">This is an automated message from mail2print.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">mail2print &mdash; Powered by CUPS</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
